  <title>Show Desktop</title>

  <p>
    The <app>Show Desktop</app> panel plugin adds an icon that, when clicked, 
    minimizes all open windows and shows the desktop. If all windows are minimized, 
    clicking the <app>Show Desktop</app> icon will restore all minimized windows.
  </p>

